author: Ken Stanford
title: Gainesville man named to state WWI Centennial Commission
text: The Da Vinci Academy (DVA) at South Hall Middle School and the Earhart-Edison Academy (E2) at North Hall Middle School have opened the application process for rising 6th graders who wish to apply to attend for the fall of 2016. 9:11AM ( 39 minutes ago ) Two wrecks on Georgia Highway 365 near Demorest-Mt. Airy Highway sent seven people to area hospitals Saturday night 9:07AM ( 43 minutes ago ) The Georgia State Patrol has released details of a head-on wreck that injured three people between Demorest and Clarkesville Saturday morning. 8:29AM ( 1 hour ago ) Local/State News
